Yaagin Aminooni sakettidabaa milatidi biidi hiixan zin77iis. Kawoi a be7anau yiido wode, Aminooni a, “Ta michchiyaa Taamaara yaada, taayyo issi lo77o oittaa ta xeellishin uukkiyaakkonne taani i kushiyaappe miyaakko dosais shin” yaagiis.
Ha77ikka ta godai kawoi ba wozanan, ‘Kawuwaa naati ubbati haiqqidosona’ yaagidi odido oduwaa tuma gooppo; Aminoona xallai haiqqiis” yaagiis.
Oichchin maccaasiyaa, “Ta godau kawuwau, ne shemppoi ero! Neeni ta godai kawoi haasayido ubbabaappe ushachchi woikko haddirssi gaanau danddayiya issi asikka baawa. Ee; hagaa tana azazidaagee, ta doonan, ne ashkkaree doonan hagaa wottidaagee ne ashkkaraa Yoo7aaba.
Kawoi kiyin, asai ubbai aara biis; biidi katamau wurssetta keettaa lanqqen eqqidosona.
