He araataa pude kiyiyo usuppun xekkatun ya baggaaranne ha baggaara issi issi gaammo misilee, muleera tammanne naa77u misileti de7oosona. Hagaa mala kawotaa araatai hara kawotettan awaaninne oosettibeenna.
Yaagin kawoi a, “Neeyyo hagan aibi pacciinee neeni ne biitti baanau koyiyoi?” yaagidi oichchiis.
I eta, “Intte tana zoriyoobi aibee? ‘Ne aawai nuna toossido deexo qambbaraa nuuyyo kaushsharkkii’ yaagiya ha deriyaayyo woigada zaaroo?” yaagidi oichchiis.
Kawoi Xoossaa asa, “Tanaara ta soo hindda; kattanne ma. Qassi taani neeyyo imotaa immana” yaagiis.
Yaagin Iyorbbaama keettaayyiyaa i giidoogaadan oottaasu; denddada Akiiya soo Seelo baasu. Akiiyi xeellanau danddayenna; i cimmido gishshau, a aifee demmenna.
Gidikkonne, appe guyyiyan Yerusalaamen kawotana malanne Yerusalaame sarotettaa naagana mala, GODAI a Xoossai Daawita gishshau Abiiyassi issi attuma na7aa immiis.
Hanaana na7aa Yeehu baggaara GODAA qaalai Baa7ishabaa hagaadan yaagiiddi yiis;
