SHin etappekka Kawoi Yoraami Sooriyaa Kawuwaa Hazaa7eelaara olettido wode, Sooriyaa biittaa asati a caddido cachchaa xalettanau Iziraa7eela katamaa yiichchiis.
“Simmi intte godaa zareti inttenaara de7iyo gishshau, qassi paratinne paraa gaareti, yuushoi gimbbettido katamatinne ola miishshati intteyyo de7iyo gishshau, ha dabddaabbee inttena gakko sohuwaarakka,
Qassikka Ba7aalau goinniyo eeqa shuchchaa kinchcherettidosona; Ba7aala eeqa keettaakka qolidosona. Yaatidi he sohuwaa sheeshsha keetta kessidosona; hachchi gakkanaashinkka he sohoi sheeshsha keetta gididi attiis.
Yo7aashi kawotiyo wode laappun laitta na7a.
