Abeet GODAU, ne ashkkaraa gishshau, ne wozanaa qofaadan ha gitabaa ubbaa oottada, ha gitatettaa ubbaa tana erissadasa.
Hegaa gishshau, asati daro yeellatidosona. Daawiti hegaa siyidi, i etaara gaittiya asa kiittiis. Kiittidi, “Intte buuchchai diccanaashin, Yarkko kataman de7ishshite; hegaappe guyyiyan haa yiite” yaagiis.
Yaagin GODAI Daawitayyo hananabaa yootiya Gaada hagaadan yaagidi haasayissiis;
“Ha77ikka ta na7au, GODAI nenaara gido. GODAI kase nebaa haasayidoogaadan, GODAA ne Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanaagaa nena polisso.
Leewa yeletan bantta zariyaaninne keettan bantta sunttan mazggafettidaageeti hageeta; laatamu laittanne hegaappe bollaara de7iya Leewa zareti ubbai GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyan oottidosona.
Yiriiyi, Amaaree, Yahaazi7eelinne Yiqami7aami Kebroona zare; eti bantta yeletaa maaran xaafettidosona.
